Package: UHHthesis
Type: Package
Title: R Markdown Templates for Bachelor or Master Thesis at the UHH
Version: 0.1.9000
Date: 2022-07-08
Authors@R: c(person("Saskia", "Otto", email="saskia.a.otto@gmail.com",
    role=c("aut","cre")))
Maintainer: Saskia Otto <saskia.a.otto@gmail.com>
Description: This package creates a bookdown project structure with German or English LaTeX and Word thesis 
    templates from the University of Hamburg (UHH), which conform to the submission standards of the MIN
    faculty for Bachelor and Master theses. The package is primarly designed for the Biology Department
    and its new 'Data Science in Biology' program. It aims aims to encourage reproducible research using simple 
    Markdown syntax while embedding all of the R code to produce plots and analyses as well. This package is 
    a customized version of the original 'thesisdown' package.
License: CC BY 4.0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R(>= 4.0.0)
Imports: 
    bookdown,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown (>= 2.14),
    R.utils,
    utils
Suggests:
    huxtable,
    kableExtra,
    tinytex (>= 0.40),
    xtable
SystemRequirements: pandoc (>= 2.1) - http://pandoc.org
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 7.2.0
